# m7f §7 negative: `import ?name` reports a clear error when the
# symbol-index v1 finds no match. The v1 index scans only known
# stdlib modules + modules already imported by name in this file;
# without `--path stdlib` on the command line, even the stdlib
# scan finds nothing — exactly the situation this fixture
# exercises.

import ?nosuchsymbol

